	     person("Simen", "Guare", role=c("ctb"),
	           email = "simen.gaure@frisch.uio.no"))
Description: R wrappers around the cubature C library of
    Steven G. Johnson for adaptive multivariate integration over hypercubes
    and the Cuba C library of Thomas Hahn. This version provides both
    hcubature and pcubature routines from the cubature library in addition
    to a vector interface that results in substantial speed gains.
